text: Seulline is a commune. It is found in the region Normandy in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. == History == The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Saint- Georges-d'Aunay and Coulvain.Arrêté préfectoral 17 December 2015 On 1 January 2017, the former commune of La Bigne was merged into Seulline.Arrêté préfectoral 26 September 2016 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Seulline
